{"tid":950959,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"在家擁抱陌生人年賺170萬　金髮妹讚「完美工作」傳遞獨特能量","createTime":"2018-12-22T02:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T03:16:26.000Z","uid":212399,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"29558f60c1c933a5687a34a22c4881cd0fdea8fc","tid":950959,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1UxmDNr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1UxmDNr.jpg&h=a1b050ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲貝茲熱愛自己的工作。（圖／翻攝IG／ceceliaailecec）&nbsp;<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n美國費城24歲女子貝茲（Cecelia Baez）有份特殊職業，她每周花費約15小時來擁抱網路上遇到的陌生人，並提供這些客戶建議，讓他們的生活變得更好。她說，「一旦我開始擁抱別人，就知道不會有回頭路，這對我來說是完美的工作。」<br />\n貝茲也是一名調酒師， 2016年她經由朋友介紹，進入專門提供客戶擁抱的公司。據了解，該網站已培訓約400位專業人員，會定期聯繫各地的客戶。貝茲提到，她的擁抱受過訓練，每小時收費約80美元（約台幣2460元），她會安慰心情不好的陌生人，同時給予各種建議，像是鼓勵對方培養新的嗜好，開始嶄新戀情。<br />\n「我喜歡激勵人們採取行動，並提出最適合他們的改變。」靠著撫慰人心，貝茲年收入達到5.5萬美元（約台幣170萬元），她回憶起初發現這種工作時就立刻想要從事，但她很緊張，肢體也相當僵硬。<br />\n隨著時間的推移，貝茲變得越來越熟練，現在她對自己的工作感到很自在，也與客人保持良好溝通。除了受訓與經過認證，她也是整合健康教練，同時致力於冥想練習，她在網站上寫道，擁抱會在她溫暖的家中進行，彼此傳遞獨特的能量。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FwdUek7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFwdUek7.jpg&h=6f0fde7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s0YtiNS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs0YtiNS.jpg&h=cbeb8d8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QjzPNGq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQjzPNGq.jpg&h=37af5e29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n染著亮麗金髮的貝茲說，她會鼓勵客戶表達自我，「我知道的越多，更能好好為你服務。」儘管她的職業經常被外界誤解，身邊的親朋好友卻是全力支持，她欣慰表示，「他們明白，觸摸對人們來說至關重要。」<br />\n貝茲觀察到，現代社會使得人們的互動變少，感覺比以往更加孤獨，「所以我很高興，我能幫助人們獲得他們生命中缺少的接觸，同時，也幫助我自己。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181222/1337403.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181222%2F1337403.htm&d=l9aZWPgK1g3ajVNLadFgETACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=1f384aa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181222/1337403.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f1efc921779a5dba384da222ac1a8713cca09f7e","tid":950959,"uid":75610,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:56:49.000Z","msg":"Free hug <br />\nPremium hug"},{"pid":"d509f69ed1e2f6b45bdd75b5974c508b322760aa","tid":950959,"uid":120728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:57:27.000Z","msg":"so hot"},{"pid":"3f28c8c6a8dc889f385cef3f15ca7c360df20db6","tid":950959,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:57:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4aab2ee21bf9ad241e28f905a412271691439257","tid":950959,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1130927a3d682f6c4f33ad9cd96b2626ab04ef0","tid":950959,"uid":62646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/-2017-10-23-8.38.33_71370130059ede93f256b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2F-2017-10-23-8.38.33_71370130059ede93f256b3.jpg&h=d8584df3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fce473c41436c60fb5acd1f12aeb227e052b8ecd","tid":950959,"uid":177089,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:00:26.000Z","msg":"起初發現這種工作時就立刻想要從事，但她很緊張，肢體也相當僵硬。<br />\n隨著時間的推移，貝茲變得越來越熟練<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9277821ba73bc2dc60a6628d62fca17dbc52e246","tid":950959,"uid":118710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03: